1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:32,799
Mr. Song,
Mr. Yu's wound has been treated.

4
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,879
Mr. Song, are you alright?

5
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,359
Ji Xuan.

6
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:46,120
Can you hold me? Just for a minute.

7
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,560
Mr. Song, did you drive?

8
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:45,240
You mean Mr. Song can't drive?

9
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,680
Six years ago,

10
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,759
Mr. Song had just gotten his license
and took his brother for a ride.

11
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,199
Then they were kidnapped.

12
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:56,439
The kidnappers held a knife
to force Mr. Song to drive.

13
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,879
His brother got killed.

14
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,479
Mr. Song was rescued,

15
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,240
but he becomes unable
to drive ever since.

16
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,329
It's all my fault

17
00:03:03,616 --> 00:03:05,632
for going to the restroom
at that critical moment.

18
00:03:09,819 --> 00:03:10,639
Ji Xuan.

19
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:15,680
Can you hold me? Just for a minute.

20
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:45,840
Mr. Song, I made you soup to soothe you.

21
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,800
Feeling better?

22
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,199
Much better.

23
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:09,000
You can't drive, why didn't you tell me?

24
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,199
The project comes first.
I can overcome it.

25
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,560
But you can't disregard your own safety.

26
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,720
Are you caring about me?

27
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,759
Let me help you rest.

28
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,560
Aren't you sleeping?

29
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,959
Not now.

30
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,552
Why are you gluing the lamp?

31
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:42,560
I heard Mrs. Yu made the lamp herself
before she passed.

32
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,720
Mr. Yu carries it wherever he goes.

33
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:49,319
While he's recuperating in the hospital,
I want to restore this lamp.

34
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:53,849
But this purple glass piece
is shattered.

35
00:04:53,849 --> 00:04:55,000
It's hard to fix.

36
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:59,319
I'll help you glue
the other pieces first.

37
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:02,120
Tomorrow,
we'll try our luck on the beach

38
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:04,519
and see if we can find purple piece.

39
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,319
(Waves as matchmaker,)

40
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,040
(sand as our bed.)

41
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:54,720
(So, no two shells
in this world are alike.)

42
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:58,160
(They've heard centuries of tides
rising and falling.)

43
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:03,360
(What they await might be
this very moment of being picked up.)

44
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,199
This shell is called Purple Glaze,

45
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:36,096
grows in the deep sea
thousands of meters down

46
00:06:36,096 --> 00:06:37,759
and is very demanding
of its environment.

47
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:40,519
There are fewer than five in the sea.
They're very rare.

48
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,839
Then where should we look for one?

49
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:47,480
Unless... Unless you dive
before the tsunami hits.

50
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:50,879
There'll be massive churning underwater
that might bring the Purple Glaze up.

51
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,160
Mr. Song.

52
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,519
Mr. Song.

53
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,879
Song Zhaoli.

54
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,800
Song Zhaoli.

55
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:51,519
(Unless... Unless you dive
before the tsunami hits.)

56
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:55,000
(There'll be massive churning underwater
that might bring the Purple Glaze up.)

57
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,920
(Is Song Zhaoli...)

58
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,800
Song Zhaoli!

59
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,720
Song Zhaoli!

60
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:09,959
Song Zhaoli!

61
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,600
Song Zhaoli!

62
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,360
Song Zhaoli!

63
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,839
Song Zhaoli!

64
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,360
Song Zhaoli!

65
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,399
Come out!

66
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,639
Come out!

67
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,399
Song Zhaoli!

68
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,000
Song Zhaoli!

69
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,360
Song Zhaoli!

70
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,799
Song Zhaoli!

71
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,679
Ji Xuan!

72
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,080
Ji Xuan!

73
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,320
I'm here.

74
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,440
I found it. Look.

75
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,799
Song Zhaoli!

76
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:14,080
Don't you know how dangerous that was?

77
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:20,840
Ji Xuan, I found it.

78
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,960
I've told you

79
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:27,039
I care more about your safety
than the project.

80
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,799
Do you understand, Song Zhaoli?

81
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,639
Ji Xuan.

82
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,919
This is the first time you cried for me.

83
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:44,480
I thought...
I thought I'd never see you again.

84
00:11:17,303 --> 00:11:19,095
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

85
00:11:19,255 --> 00:11:21,135
♪Flickering neon lights♪

86
00:11:21,335 --> 00:11:24,663
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

87
00:11:25,175 --> 00:11:27,447
♪Every star is♪

88
00:11:27,735 --> 00:11:31,607
♪My heartbeat for you♪

89
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:34,743
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

90
00:11:34,903 --> 00:11:36,455
♪And land in your arms♪

91
00:11:36,855 --> 00:11:40,311
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

92
00:11:40,567 --> 00:11:43,127
♪In the blue sky♪

93
00:11:43,191 --> 00:11:47,319
♪Your smile still lingers♪

94
00:11:48,247 --> 00:11:51,895
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

95
00:11:52,151 --> 00:11:55,815
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

96
00:11:56,023 --> 00:11:58,935
♪Can't find a cure♪

97
00:11:58,935 --> 00:12:03,447
♪To love you after we've parted♪

98
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:07,671
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

99
00:12:07,671 --> 00:12:11,535
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

100
00:12:11,535 --> 00:12:13,335
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

101
00:12:13,431 --> 00:12:18,583
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

102
00:12:19,223 --> 00:12:22,935
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

103
00:12:23,127 --> 00:12:25,879
♪Can't find a cure♪

104
00:12:26,007 --> 00:12:30,647
♪To love you after we've parted♪

105
00:12:30,815 --> 00:12:34,583
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

106
00:12:34,807 --> 00:12:38,391
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

107
